{
  "info": {
    "name": "TravelHub Notifications — QA Suite",
    "description": "Colección para probar notification-services.\n\n## Configuración (variables de la colección)\n- `base_url`: URL del servicio (default: PROD direct https://notification-services-qhweqfkejq-uc.a.run.app)\n- `internal_token`: valor del secret `prod-travelhub-internal-notify-token`\n- `user_id`: UUID del destinatario, debe tener `notification_preference` configurada en BD\n\n## Estructura\n- **Health** — endpoints públicos sin auth\n- **Internal (pms_sync)** — 3 tipos: requieren `X-Internal-Token`. Schema: `{type, user_id, hotel_id, details, recipients}`\n- **Admin Test Event (kafka simulado)** — 7 tipos: requieren `ADMIN_TEST_ENDPOINT_ENABLED=true` en PROD + `X-Internal-Token`. Schema: `{event_type, user_id, payload}`\n\n## Cómo activar el endpoint admin en PROD (1 sola vez)\n```bash\ngcloud run services update notification-services \\\n  --project=travelhub-prod-492116 --region=us-central1 \\\n  --update-env-vars=ADMIN_TEST_ENDPOINT_ENABLED=true\n```\n\nPara desactivar después de probar:\n```bash\ngcloud run services update notification-services \\\n  --project=travelhub-prod-492116 --region=us-central1 \\\n  --update-env-vars=ADMIN_TEST_ENDPOINT_ENABLED=false\n```",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "base_url",
      "value": "https://notification-services-qhweqfkejq-uc.a.run.app",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "internal_token",
      "value": "REPLACE_WITH_SECRET_FROM_GCP",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "user_id",
      "value": "b3949db6-e101-45d4-83d4-9d81ce1eda3c",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "hotel_id",
      "value": "11111111-2222-3333-4444-555555555555",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Health",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "GET /health",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/health",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["health"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "GET /ready",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/ready",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["ready"]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Internal (pms_sync)",
      "description": "Endpoint POST /api/v1/notifications/internal — para los 3 tipos pms_sync_*. NO se puede usar para booking/payment/user.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "pms_sync_complete",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"},
              {"key": "X-Internal-Token", "value": "{{internal_token}}"}
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"type\": \"pms_sync_complete\",\n  \"user_id\": \"{{user_id}}\",\n  \"hotel_id\": \"{{hotel_id}}\",\n  \"details\": {\n    \"hotel_name\": \"Hotel Tequendama\",\n    \"sync_count\": 42,\n    \"duration_ms\": 1850,\n    \"next_sync_at\": \"2026-05-13T20:00:00Z\"\n  },\n  \"recipients\": [\"hotel_admin\"]\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/notifications/internal",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "notifications", "internal"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "pms_sync_conflict",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"},
              {"key": "X-Internal-Token", "value": "{{internal_token}}"}
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"type\": \"pms_sync_conflict\",\n  \"user_id\": \"{{user_id}}\",\n  \"hotel_id\": \"{{hotel_id}}\",\n  \"details\": {\n    \"hotel_name\": \"Hotel Tequendama\",\n    \"conflict_type\": \"Doble reserva\",\n    \"description\": \"Habitación 'Suite Junior' tiene 2 reservas para 2026-06-15\"\n  },\n  \"recipients\": [\"hotel_admin\"]\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/notifications/internal",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "notifications", "internal"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "pms_sync_error",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"},
              {"key": "X-Internal-Token", "value": "{{internal_token}}"}
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"type\": \"pms_sync_error\",\n  \"user_id\": \"{{user_id}}\",\n  \"hotel_id\": \"{{hotel_id}}\",\n  \"details\": {\n    \"hotel_name\": \"Hotel Tequendama\",\n    \"error\": \"Connection timeout to pms-api.example.com after 30s\",\n    \"last_attempt_at\": \"2026-05-13T13:55:00Z\",\n    \"retry_count\": 3\n  },\n  \"recipients\": [\"hotel_admin\"]\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/notifications/internal",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "notifications", "internal"]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
